# 🌦 Weather App

A simple and intuitive weather app that provides real-time weather updates for cities worldwide. Built with modern web technologies to ensure a smooth and responsive user experience.

## 🚀 Features

- 🌍 **Global Weather Updates**: Search for weather information in any city worldwide.
- ⏱ **Real-Time Data**: Get current weather conditions, temperature, and more.
- 📅 **Forecast**: View a 5-day weather forecast.
- 🎨 **User-Friendly Interface**: Clean and responsive design for seamless usage.
- 📱 **Mobile-Optimized**: Works on both desktop and mobile devices.

## 🔧 Technologies Used

- **HTML**: For the structure of the website.
- **CSS**: For styling and layout.
- **JavaScript**: For interactive features and API integration.
- **Weather API**: [OpenWeatherMap](https://openweathermap.org/) (or specify the API you used).

## 🖥 Live Demo

Check out the live version of the app:  
[Weather App](https://Gama-3ffect.github.io/weather-app/)

## 🌐 Usage

1. Open the app in your browser.
2. Enter the name of a city in the search bar.
3. Click **Search** to view the current weather details.
4. Optional: Check the 5-day forecast.

